Ask HN: How will dev tools change in the next 5 years?
text:
Was discussing with a friend that a lot of dev tooling we use (terminals, package managers, hosting.etc) was built several years ago and hasn't kept up with modern tech stacks.

What fundamental tech stack/dev tool innovations will change the way software is built over the next 5 years?
